>\r\n<p>本社、静岡支社で開催可能です。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"topicDigestPhoto\">\r\n<a href=\"https://www.tax-iwasaki.com/recruit/post/information/\" title=\"会社見学随時募集中です！【対象：学生】\" target=\"\"><img src=\"/images/outline/numazu-office.jpg\" alt=\"会社見学随時募集中です！【対象：学生】\" /></a>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"topicsDigestBox\">\r\n<div class=\"topicDigestImgOn clearfix\">\r\n<div class=\"topicDigestText\">\r\n<p class=\"topicDate\">2026.01.15</p>\r\n<h4 class=\"topicLink\"><a href=\"/recruit/news/2026/95791/\" title=\"2/22 ぬまJOBフェアに出展します！【対象：新卒・中途】\" target=\"_self\">2/22 ぬまJOBフェアに出展します！【対象：新卒・中途】</a></h4>\r\n<p>2026年2月22日(日)　プラサヴェルデ</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"topicDigestPhoto\">\r\n<a href=\"/recruit/news/2026/95791/\" title=\"2/22 ぬまJOBフェアに出展します！【対象：新卒・中途】\" target=\"_self\"><img src=\"/images/recruit/event/images20251212095029.png\" alt=\"2/22 ぬまJOBフェアに出展します！【対象：新卒・中途】\" /></a>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"topicsDigestBox\">\r\n<div class=\"topicDigestImgOn clearfix\">\r\n<div class=\"topicDigestText\">\r\n<p class=\"topicDate\">2026.01.14</p>\r\n<h4 class=\"topicLink\"><a href=\"/recruit/news/2026/95792/\" title=\"1/31 シゴトフェアに出展します！【対象：新卒・中途】\" target=\"_self\">1/31 シゴトフェアに出展します！【対象：新卒・中途】</a></h4>\r\n<p>2026年1月31日(土)　キラメッセぬまづ</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"topicDigestPhoto\">\r\n<a href=\"/recruit/news/2026/95792/\" title=\"1/31 シゴトフェアに出展します！【対象：新卒・中途】\" target=\"_self\"><img src=\"/images/recruit/event/images20260114102659.png\" alt=\"1/31 シゴトフェアに出展します！【対象：新卒・中途】\" /></a>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div></div>\r\n<div class=\"topicDigestLink\"><a href=\"/recruit/news/\">過去一覧を見る</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<center><a href=\"./recruit\"><img src=\"/images/recruit/btn_to_recruit_top2.png\"></a></center>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"freeParts\">\r\n    <div class=\"box\">\r\n        <div class=\"boxTop\">\r\n            <div class=\"boxBottom\">\r\n                <h2>アクセス</h2>\r\n<div class=\" access-map-02\"><!-- .parts_text_type07 -->\